HERE IN DOWNTOWN DALLAS, DART'S

14:17.123 --> 14:19.092
FOUR LIGHT RAIL LINES CONVERGE,

14:19.092 --> 14:20.727
AND THIS IS ONE OF THEIR BUSIEST

14:20.727 --> 14:21.661
STATIONS.

