ABOUT 100,000 RIDERS USE THE

14:23.730 --> 14:26.265
LIGHT RAIL EACH WEEKDAY, BUT

14:26.265 --> 14:27.633
THAT'S IN A REGION OF MORE THAN

14:27.633 --> 14:29.168
SIX MILLION PEOPLE.

